1. Co 3 cach viet css trong html
- Cach 1: Viet trong thuoc tinh style cua html (code inline)
- Cach 2: viet trong the <style>
2. Id va class
-Moi id chi xuat hien 1 lan
-Moi class xuat hien nhieu lan
3. Do uu tien
- Trong cung 1 do uu tien thi css phia duoi se de phia tren, css o cuoi cung se co do uu tien cao nhat
- Khi su dung bo chon thi cang goi truc tiep thi do uu tien css cang thap
- Cac bo chon trong css la ngang hang nhau
4. CSS co ban
- font-family:chon font chu 
- font-size: chon co chu
- font-weight: chon chu dam nhat
- font-style: (italic): chu thang hoac nghieng
- text-decoration: gach chan
- color: mau chu
- line height: do cao khoi
- background color: mau nen
5. Box model
- La cach mo ta cac thanh phan ve khong gian cua 1 the html
a. Do rong cua the
- La khong gian thuc ma the html do co
- Do rong thuc la noi bat dau cua noi dung trong the
b. Padding
- Padding la thanh phan cua the html
- Noi dung the se khong nam ra pham vi cua padding nhung mau nen thi co
c. Boder
- cung la 1 thanh phan cua the html
6. Don vi
- px: don vi tuyet doi
- %: don vi tuong doi
- rem
- em: 1em = font-size cua the dang set
